					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p54285">A bunch of weird, intricate questions.</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=54285#p54285"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Tue Dec 22, 2009 4:59 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
